#L_D3_ans40=Good, do it. Greyhair, how do you think where law enforcers might take Cleric to, when they find him?
#L_D3_msg50=To their base, most likely. Come on, boss, you're not going to attack the base, are you? We might as well shoot each other instead - won't be as painful.
